    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯进军 乌克兰撤出战略要地部分地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/ukraine-retreats-from-part-of-strategic-town-as-russia-advances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰军队从顿涅茨克地区东部一个陷入战斗的城镇撤退，这是对这一战略要地的一次部分撤退，标志着阻止俄罗斯推进的斗争遭遇挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/ukraine-retreats-from-part-of-strategic-town-as-russia-advances</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 10:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京推动与中国结盟的新安全秩序，挑战美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/putin-pushes-new-china-aligned-security-order-to-challenge-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统普京提出了新的欧亚安全架构的建议，该架构以莫斯科与北京日益加深的协约为基础，旨在挑战由美国及其盟友主导的后冷战欧洲秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/putin-pushes-new-china-aligned-security-order-to-challenge-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 10:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟决定对中国电动汽车进口征收临时关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/eu-moves-ahead-with-provisional-tariffs-on-ev-imports-from-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟推进对从中国进口的电动汽车征收临时关税的计划，税率最高将提高至 48%，此举可能会加剧与北京的贸易紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/eu-moves-ahead-with-provisional-tariffs-on-ev-imports-from-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 09:07:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政界领袖警告混乱，勒庞竞争对手势头强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/le-pen-s-rivals-gain-momentum-as-political-leaders-warn-of-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周日的立法选举之前，各政党为阻止玛丽娜·勒庞的极右翼国民联盟执政而做出的最后一搏获得了动力，关键政治人物警告选民，他们的决定将彻底改变法国，并可能导致混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/le-pen-s-rivals-gain-momentum-as-political-leaders-warn-of-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:18:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚确定选举日期考验执政党团结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/romania-sets-key-election-dates-in-test-to-ruling-parties-unity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚执政党就选举时间表争论了数周，最终决定将选举定于今年晚些时候举行，这也暴露了执政两年的权力分享政府存在裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/romania-sets-key-election-dates-in-test-to-ruling-parties-unity</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:53:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大在美国报复威胁下实施数字服务税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-enacts-digital-services-tax-despite-us-retaliation-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国警告称将采取贸易报复措施，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的政府仍批准对大型外国科技公司征收数字服务税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-enacts-digital-services-tax-despite-us-retaliation-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
